This is my plan on how to achieve a healthy sleep rhythm. To specify this more precisly here is what I mean by this: get in bed by 9 pm and wake up by 5 am. I hope to achive this by following steps:
1. Get your tasks done #  create a todo-list by hand on paper  make sure to check complete tasks   use the pomodoro method to learn  mix different subjects add pe and playing the piano after long tasks
summary: This is my plan on how to achieve a healthy sleep rhythm.
